name: Rewind (itch) (Nate41223)
description:
Was produced for Weekly Game Jam #42

Theme = "Time Travel" 

WASD to move.

The objective is to get the dog to a piece of cake.

If a cactus is hit, the game rewinds time and places the dog at a point in the past.

Careful not to go too fast! its Slippery!
